---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`CV - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Professional experience, projects, and education" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>CV</h1>

			<section>
				<h2>Professional Experience</h2>

				<div class="entry">
					<div class="entry-header">
						<div>
							<h3>10Pines</h3>
							<span class="role">Software Developer, DevOps Engineer, SRE</span>
						</div>
						<div class="meta">
							<span class="date">Jul 2016 - May 2025</span>
							<span class="location">Buenos Aires, Argentina</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>
						At this horizontal company I wore many hats beyond writing code. I ran the mentoring
						program for new hires and helped shape company culture. On the infrastructure side,
						I built an internal developer platform on Kubernetes using ArgoCD, Helm, and Grafana
						after migrating off Heroku, and led the migration from a homegrown OAuth2 solution
						to OIDC across multiple languages and frameworks.
					</p>
					<p>Some of the client projects I worked on:</p>
					<ul class="projects-list">
						<li><strong>Richeta</strong> — Trained and coached a team in Elixir, Phoenix, and LiveView for a CRM rewrite.</li>
						<li><strong>Spring by Amaze</strong> — Migrated a Rails monolith from EC2 to EKS with ingress-nginx, ArgoCD, Helm, and Terraform.</li>
						<li><strong>Telecom</strong> — Migrated a BFF from Java on OpenShift to Node.js + TypeScript on ECS and Lambda.</li>
						<li><strong>Ordo</strong> — Built a staging environment for pre-production testing on GKE with ArgoCD and GitOps.</li>
						<li><strong>Hoopla</strong> — Managed 25+ microservices infrastructure and migrated from EC2 to Kubernetes for cost reduction.</li>
						<li><strong>Hero Motorcycles</strong> — Built an online motorcycle sales system with Elixir, Phoenix, and React.</li>
						<li><strong>Aquabyte</strong> — Built an ML pipeline to detect fish health issues, isolated via Docker.</li>
						<li><strong>Cardboardit.com</strong> — Built a user story mapping app with Jira/Rally/TFS/Pivotal integrations and real-time sync.</li>
						<li><strong>Income Tax Calculator</strong> — Built an employee tax forecasting tool with Haskell, Elm, and a CI/CD pipeline.</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="tags">
						<span>Kubernetes</span><span>Elixir</span><span>Haskell</span><span>Ruby on Rails</span>
						<span>TypeScript</span><span>Node.js</span><span>AWS</span><span>GCP</span>
						<span>ArgoCD</span><span>Docker</span><span>Helm</span><span>Terraform</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="entry">
					<div class="entry-header">
						<div>
							<h3>Mulesoft Inc.</h3>
							<span class="role">Software Developer</span>
						</div>
						<div class="meta">
							<span class="date">Sep 2015 - Mar 2016</span>
							<span class="location">Buenos Aires, Argentina</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>Developed a RESTful API for a CMS with integrations into microservices and the Eclipse IDE.</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span>JavaScript</span><span>Node.js</span><span>Express</span><span>AWS</span><span>AngularJS</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="entry">
					<div class="entry-header">
						<div>
							<h3>Freelance</h3>
							<span class="role">Web Developer</span>
						</div>
						<div class="meta">
							<span class="date">Apr 2015 - Sep 2015</span>
							<span class="location">Buenos Aires, Argentina</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>Built a web-based career counseling application, handling the full project lifecycle.</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span>Python</span><span>Django</span><span>Ansible</span><span>Nginx</span><span>DigitalOcean</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="entry">
					<div class="entry-header">
						<div>
							<h3>Ozono Informatica</h3>
							<span class="role">IT Support</span>
						</div>
						<div class="meta">
							<span class="date">Sep 2014 - Mar 2015</span>
							<span class="location">Buenos Aires, Argentina</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>Maintained Windows systems, configured pfSense as a load balancer, managed Xen virtual machines, and containerized on-prem apps.</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span>Docker</span><span>Linux</span><span>pfSense</span><span>Windows</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="entry">
					<div class="entry-header">
						<div>
							<h3>Toteming SA</h3>
							<span class="role">Developer</span>
						</div>
						<div class="meta">
							<span class="date">Jan 2014 - Jul 2014</span>
							<span class="location">Buenos Aires, Argentina</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>Developed an event marketing system with RFID wristbands, an Android app, and a web UI.</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span>Java</span><span>Android</span><span>PHP</span><span>Python</span><span>MySQL</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Projects</h2>

				<div class="entry">
					<div class="entry-header">
						<div>
							<h3>HaskellBA</h3>
							<span class="role">Organizer & Speaker</span>
						</div>
						<div class="meta">
							<span class="date">2017 - Present</span>
							<span class="location">Buenos Aires, Argentina</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>Organize and occasionally deliver talks on Haskell and functional programming.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="entry">
					<div class="entry-header">
						<div>
							<h3>Conferer</h3>
							<span class="role">Developer</span>
						</div>
						<div class="meta">
							<span class="date">2023 - Present</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>
						Open source Haskell library for managing application configuration.
						Features a robust CI pipeline tested against multiple GHC versions.
					</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span>Haskell</span><span>Servant</span><span>Docker</span><span>Open Source</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="entry">
					<div class="entry-header">
						<div>
							<h3>Banana Split</h3>
							<span class="role">Developer</span>
						</div>
						<div class="meta">
							<span class="date">2023 - Present</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>
						Open source expense-splitting app similar to Splitwise with additional features.
						Deployed on a personal Kubernetes cluster with Helm and ArgoCD, using pgroll for
						zero-downtime database migrations.
					</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span>Haskell</span><span>Elm</span><span>Postgres</span><span>Kubernetes</span><span>Open Source</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="entry">
					<div class="entry-header">
						<div>
							<h3>NixOS Configuration</h3>
							<span class="role">Developer</span>
						</div>
						<div class="meta">
							<span class="date">2024 - Present</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>Open source NixOS configuration for my personal systems.</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span>Nix</span><span>NixOS</span><span>Open Source</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Education</h2>

				<div class="entry">
					<div class="entry-header">
						<div>
							<h3>University of Buenos Aires</h3>
							<span class="role">Bachelor in Computer Science</span>
						</div>
						<div class="meta">
							<span class="date">2014 -</span>
							<span class="location">Argentina</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Languages</h2>
				<ul class="languages">
					<li><strong>Spanish</strong> — Native</li>
					<li><strong>English</strong> — Advanced</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5em;
	}

	section h2 {
		border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
		padding-bottom: 0.3em;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}

	.entry {
		margin-bottom: 2em;
	}

	.entry-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: baseline;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5em;
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}

	.entry-header h3 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.3em;
	}

	.role {
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.95em;
	}

	.meta {
		text-align: right;
		font-size: 0.9em;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
	}

	.meta .location {
		display: block;
	}

	.entry p {
		margin: 0.3em 0 0.5em;
	}

	.projects-list {
		margin: 0.5em 0;
		padding-left: 1.2em;
	}

	.projects-list li {
		margin-bottom: 0.3em;
		font-size: 0.95em;
	}

	.tags {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.4em;
		margin-top: 0.5em;
	}

	.tags span {
		background: rgb(var(--gray-light));
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		padding: 0.15em 0.6em;
		border-radius: 4px;
		font-size: 0.8em;
	}

	.languages {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.languages li {
		margin-bottom: 0.3em;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.entry-header {
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.meta {
			text-align: left;
		}
	}
</style>
